{
  "texts": [
    "The DA recommendations are then validated through laboratory experiments.",
    "The results of these validations are fed back to the DA to refine and improve its future material design proposals based on empirical evidence.",
    "The second variant shown in Figure 2, the TVDL, uses a TTverifier workflow as proposed by Cobe et al. [28] and Lightman et al.",
    "This workflow extends the SFDL by generating additional test designs and a VM that scores each proposal in a second forward prediction loop.",
    "The fundamental difference between the DA and the VM lies in the direction of their predictions."
  ]
}